They also demanded a legal guarantee on Minimum Support Prices (MSP) for their crops.

Mount Tam's fog wave. This day's fog is a bit thicker than those days when you can kind of see the road leading up to the mountain (Panoramic Highway). But the shape of the fog looks quite interesting still.

description:
Great experience in a beautiful place.
StarsBOX is more than a nest: it is a synthesis of shelter and travel, a dream box where you can get drunk on stars and light up with fresh dawns. 
Half tent, half hut, it offers protection but can also open up to the sky to display all that nature has to offer in terms of aesthetics.
It was born at high altitude but can be placed anywhere; it knows how to cuddle its guests under the starry vault.
StarsBOX is a fairy tale that lasts for a whole night, a creativity exercise of simple and childlike genuineness.
